definition: he or him/(used for either sex when the sex is unknown or unimportant)/(used before sb's name for emphasis)/(used as a meaningless mock object)/other/another

sentences.english: "More than any other subject, weight is delicate, " Maddison said.
sentences.chinese: “体重问题比其他问题都要微妙，”麦迪逊说。

sentences.english: Some other drugs have to be taken on an empty stomach.
sentences.chinese: 而其他某些药物，必须在空腹服用。

sentences.english: A blindly ending branch of the alimentary canal or other organ.
sentences.chinese: 消化道或其他器官分支的盲端。

sentences.english: The acids in tomato juice can degrade the drink’s other ingredients.
sentences.chinese: 番茄汁中的酸会削弱其他材料带来的味觉。

sentences.english: Have Chesapeake and other natural-gas producers survived the worst of the crisis?
sentences.chinese: 切萨皮克以及其他的天然气公司真的挺过来了吗？

sentences.english: Applicants should not be receiving any other bursary schemes.
sentences.chinese: 申请者不应是其他助学金计划的领受者。

sentences.english: The horse's strides are shorter than at the other canters, without losing elasticity and cadence.
sentences.chinese: 马的步幅比其他几种跑步较短，但却不失弹性与节奏。

sentences.english: It is believed that the sperm whale dives deeper than any other cetacean.
sentences.chinese: 人们相信，抹香鲸比其他鲸类动物潜得更深。

sentences.english: It took only a short walk on a Beijing street to find other foreigners.
sentences.chinese: 我在北京街头仅走了一小段路来寻找其他的外国人。

sentences.english: He shows up in other people and what they say to you.
sentences.chinese: 他以其他人的形式出现，这些人对你说什么？

sentences.english: All these facilities help society reduce the generation gap between the elderly and the others.
sentences.chinese: 这可以协助缩小老人和其他人之间的代沟。

sentences.english: Unlike most other fish, they are monogamous and mate for life.
sentences.chinese: 不像其他的鱼类，它们是一夫一妻制并终生厮守。

sentences.english: Chinese culture sees all non-Chinese as sub-human, to be exploited.
sentences.chinese: 中国文化把所有的其他人种视为有待剥削的次等民族。

sentences.english: Gahl: The NT5E gene is like many other genes.
sentences.chinese: NT5E基因像许多其他基因一样。

sentences.english: But users also ask about current events and many other subjects.
sentences.chinese: 但是用户也会问及时事和许多其他的问题。

definition: other/the others/else/other than it/in addition to the thing mentioned above
apart from/other than/except for/external/outside of/on the other side of/beyond
to combine a powdery substance (flour, plaster etc) with water/Taiwan pr. [huo4]
to compose a poem in reply (to sb's poem) using the same rhyme sequence/to join in the singing/to chime in with others
to mix (ingredients) together/to blend/classifier for rinses of clothes/classifier for boilings of medicinal herbs
to complete a set in mahjong or playing cards
and/together with/with/sum/union/peace/harmony/Taiwan pr. [han4] when it means "and" or "with"
of/~'s (possessive particle)/(used after an attribute)/(used to form a nominal expression)/(used at the end of a declarative sentence for emphasis)
to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
